              "[?!1>failOld;][?1 < failOld;trepair:=t;++?!1 < failOld;]((0<=ai&ai<=iMAX()&as>=0&as<=sMAX()&TS()>=c&c>=0&(1=0|1=1))&h-as*(TS()-c)>=hMIN()&((ai-as)*TS() < RR()*TS()->h+(0-as)*(TS()-c)>=hDEG()&as=sMAX())&(1=0&(ai-as)*TS()>=RR()*TS()->h>=hMIN()+RR()*(t-trepair)|as>=sDEG()&h>=hDEG())&(1=0&as < sDEG()->t-trepair+(TS()-c) < tREPDEG())&0>=0&(1=0->0=ai))//[?1 < failOld;trepair:=t;]((0<=ai&ai<=iMAX()&as>=0&as<=sMAX()&TS()>=c&c>=0&(1=0|1=1))&h-as*(TS()-c)>=hMIN()&((ai-as)*TS() < RR()*TS()->h+(0-as)*(TS()-c)>=hDEG()&as=sMAX())&(1=0&(ai-as)*TS()>=RR()*TS()->h>=hMIN()+RR()*(t-trepair)|as>=sDEG()&h>=hDEG())&(1=0&as < sDEG()->t-trepair+(TS()-c) < tREPDEG())&0>=0&(1=0->0=ai))":
                unfold;
                fullSimplify;
                QE,
              "[?!0>failOld;][?0 < failOld;trepair:=t;++?!0 < failOld;]((0<=ai&ai<=iMAX()&as>=0&as<=sMAX()&TS()>=c&c>=0&(0=0|0=1))&h-as*(TS()-c)>=hMIN()&((ai-as)*TS() < RR()*TS()->h+(0-as)*(TS()-c)>=hDEG()&as=sMAX())&(0=0&(ai-as)*TS()>=RR()*TS()->h>=hMIN()+RR()*(t-trepair)|as>=sDEG()&h>=hDEG())&(0=0&as < sDEG()->t-trepair+(TS()-c) < tREPDEG())&min(iMAX(),ai)>=0&(0=0->min(iMAX(),ai)=ai))//[?0 < failOld;trepair:=t;]((0<=ai&ai<=iMAX()&as>=0&as<=sMAX()&TS()>=c&c>=0&(0=0|0=1))&h-as*(TS()-c)>=hMIN()&((ai-as)*TS() < RR()*TS()->h+(0-as)*(TS()-c)>=hDEG()&as=sMAX())&(0=0&(ai-as)*TS()>=RR()*TS()->h>=hMIN()+RR()*(t-trepair)|as>=sDEG()&h>=hDEG())&(0=0&as < sDEG()->t-trepair+(TS()-c) < tREPDEG())&min(iMAX(),ai)>=0&(0=0->min(iMAX(),ai)=ai))":
                unfold;
                fullSimplify;
                QE,
              "[?!0>failOld;][?0 < failOld;trepair:=t;++?!0 < failOld;]((0<=ai&ai<=iMAX()&as>=0&as<=sMAX()&TS()>=c&c>=0&(0=0|0=1))&h-as*(TS()-c)>=hMIN()&((ai-as)*TS() < RR()*TS()->h+(0-as)*(TS()-c)>=hDEG()&as=sMAX())&(0=0&(ai-as)*TS()>=RR()*TS()->h>=hMIN()+RR()*(t-trepair)|as>=sDEG()&h>=hDEG())&(0=0&as < sDEG()->t-trepair+(TS()-c) < tREPDEG())&min(iMAX(),ai)>=0&(0=0->min(iMAX(),ai)=ai))//[?!0 < failOld;]((0<=ai&ai<=iMAX()&as>=0&as<=sMAX()&TS()>=c&c>=0&(0=0|0=1))&h-as*(TS()-c)>=hMIN()&((ai-as)*TS() < RR()*TS()->h+(0-as)*(TS()-c)>=hDEG()&as=sMAX())&(0=0&(ai-as)*TS()>=RR()*TS()->h>=hMIN()+RR()*(t-trepair)|as>=sDEG()&h>=hDEG())&(0=0&as < sDEG()->t-trepair+(TS()-c) < tREPDEG())&min(iMAX(),ai)>=0&(0=0->min(iMAX(),ai)=ai))":
                unfold;
                fullSimplify;
                QE,
              "[?!1>failOld;][?1 < failOld;trepair:=t;++?!1 < failOld;]((0<=ai&ai<=iMAX()&as>=0&as<=sMAX()&TS()>=c&c>=0&(1=0|1=1))&h-as*(TS()-c)>=hMIN()&((ai-as)*TS() < RR()*TS()->h+(0-as)*(TS()-c)>=hDEG()&as=sMAX())&(1=0&(ai-as)*TS()>=RR()*TS()->h>=hMIN()+RR()*(t-trepair)|as>=sDEG()&h>=hDEG())&(1=0&as < sDEG()->t-trepair+(TS()-c) < tREPDEG())&0>=0&(1=0->0=ai))//[?!1 < failOld;]((0<=ai&ai<=iMAX()&as>=0&as<=sMAX()&TS()>=c&c>=0&(1=0|1=1))&h-as*(TS()-c)>=hMIN()&((ai-as)*TS() < RR()*TS()->h+(0-as)*(TS()-c)>=hDEG()&as=sMAX())&(1=0&(ai-as)*TS()>=RR()*TS()->h>=hMIN()+RR()*(t-trepair)|as>=sDEG()&h>=hDEG())&(1=0&as < sDEG()->t-trepair+(TS()-c) < tREPDEG())&0>=0&(1=0->0=ai))":
                unfold;
                fullSimplify;
                QE,
              "[?1>failOld;tfail:=t;hfail:=h;sfail:=as;][?1 < failOld;trepair:=t;++?!1 < failOld;]((0<=ai&ai<=iMAX()&as>=0&as<=sMAX()&TS()>=c&c>=0&(1=0|1=1))&h-as*(TS()-c)>=hMIN()&((ai-as)*TS() < RR()*TS()->h+(0-as)*(TS()-c)>=hDEG()&as=sMAX())&(1=0&(ai-as)*TS()>=RR()*TS()->h>=hMIN()+RR()*(t-trepair)|as>=sDEG()&h>=hDEG())&(1=0&as < sDEG()->t-trepair+(TS()-c) < tREPDEG())&0>=0&(1=0->0=ai))//[?!1 < failOld;]((0<=ai&ai<=iMAX()&as>=0&as<=sMAX()&TS()>=c&c>=0&(1=0|1=1))&h-as*(TS()-c)>=hMIN()&((ai-as)*TS() < RR()*TS()->h+(0-as)*(TS()-c)>=hDEG()&as=sMAX())&(1=0&(ai-as)*TS()>=RR()*TS()->h>=hMIN()+RR()*(t-trepair)|as>=sDEG()&h>=hDEG())&(1=0&as < sDEG()->t-trepair+(TS()-c) < tREPDEG())&0>=0&(1=0->0=ai))":
                unfold;
                fullSimplify;
                QE,
              "[?0>failOld;tfail:=t;hfail:=h;sfail:=as;][?0 < failOld;trepair:=t;++?!0 < failOld;]((0<=ai&ai<=iMAX()&as>=0&as<=sMAX()&TS()>=c&c>=0&(0=0|0=1))&h-as*(TS()-c)>=hMIN()&((ai-as)*TS() < RR()*TS()->h+(0-as)*(TS()-c)>=hDEG()&as=sMAX())&(0=0&(ai-as)*TS()>=RR()*TS()->h>=hMIN()+RR()*(t-trepair)|as>=sDEG()&h>=hDEG())&(0=0&as < sDEG()->t-trepair+(TS()-c) < tREPDEG())&min(iMAX(),ai)>=0&(0=0->min(iMAX(),ai)=ai))//[?!0 < failOld;]((0<=ai&ai<=iMAX()&as>=0&as<=sMAX()&TS()>=c&c>=0&(0=0|0=1))&h-as*(TS()-c)>=hMIN()&((ai-as)*TS() < RR()*TS()->h+(0-as)*(TS()-c)>=hDEG()&as=sMAX())&(0=0&(ai-as)*TS()>=RR()*TS()->h>=hMIN()+RR()*(t-trepair)|as>=sDEG()&h>=hDEG())&(0=0&as < sDEG()->t-trepair+(TS()-c) < tREPDEG())&min(iMAX(),ai)>=0&(0=0->min(iMAX(),ai)=ai))":
                unfold;
                fullSimplify;
                QE
            )
        ),
      "Show [a]Q":
        unfold;
        boxAnd('R=="[{t'=1,c'=1,h'=i-d&c<=TS()}]((0<=ai&ai<=iMAX()&as>=0&as<=sMAX()&TS()>=c&c>=0&(fail=0|fail=1))&h-as*(TS()-c)>=hMIN()&((ai-as)*TS() < RR()*TS()->h+(0-as)*(TS()-c)>=hDEG()&as=sMAX())&(fail=0&(ai-as)*TS()>=RR()*TS()->h>=hMIN()+RR()*(t-trepair)|as>=sDEG()&h>=hDEG())&(fail=0&as < sDEG()->t-trepair+(TS()-c) < tREPDEG()))");
        andR('R=="[{t'=1,c'=1,h'=i-d&c<=TS()}](0<=ai&ai<=iMAX()&as>=0&as<=sMAX()&TS()>=c&c>=0&(fail=0|fail=1))&[{t'=1,c'=1,h'=i-d&c<=TS()}](h-as*(TS()-c)>=hMIN()&((ai-as)*TS() < RR()*TS()->h+(0-as)*(TS()-c)>=hDEG()&as=sMAX())&(fail=0&(ai-as)*TS()>=RR()*TS()->h>=hMIN()+RR()*(t-trepair)|as>=sDEG()&h>=hDEG())&(fail=0&as < sDEG()->t-trepair+(TS()-c) < tREPDEG()))"); <(
          "[{t'=1,c'=1,h'=i-d&c<=TS()}](0<=ai&ai<=iMAX()&as>=0&as<=sMAX()&TS()>=c&c>=0&(fail=0|fail=1))":
            auto,
          "[{t'=1,c'=1,h'=i-d&c<=TS()}](h-as*(TS()-c)>=hMIN()&((ai-as)*TS() < RR()*TS()->h+(0-as)*(TS()-c)>=hDEG()&as=sMAX())&(fail=0&(ai-as)*TS()>=RR()*TS()->h>=hMIN()+RR()*(t-trepair)|as>=sDEG()&h>=hDEG())&(fail=0&as < sDEG()->t-trepair+(TS()-c) < tREPDEG()))":
            boxAnd('R=="[{t'=1,c'=1,h'=i-d&c<=TS()}](h-as*(TS()-c)>=hMIN()&((ai-as)*TS() < RR()*TS()->h+(0-as)*(TS()-c)>=hDEG()&as=sMAX())&(fail=0&(ai-as)*TS()>=RR()*TS()->h>=hMIN()+RR()*(t-trepair)|as>=sDEG()&h>=hDEG())&(fail=0&as < sDEG()->t-trepair+(TS()-c) < tREPDEG()))");
            andR('R=="[{t'=1,c'=1,h'=i-d&c<=TS()}]h-as*(TS()-c)>=hMIN()&[{t'=1,c'=1,h'=i-d&c<=TS()}](((ai-as)*TS() < RR()*TS()->h+(0-as)*(TS()-c)>=hDEG()&as=sMAX())&(fail=0&(ai-as)*TS()>=RR()*TS()->h>=hMIN()+RR()*(t-trepair)|as>=sDEG()&h>=hDEG())&(fail=0&as < sDEG()->t-trepair+(TS()-c) < tREPDEG()))"); <(
              "[{t'=1,c'=1,h'=i-d&c<=TS()}]h-as*(TS()-c)>=hMIN()":
                auto,
              "[{t'=1,c'=1,h'=i-d&c<=TS()}](((ai-as)*TS() < RR()*TS()->h+(0-as)*(TS()-c)>=hDEG()&as=sMAX())&(fail=0&(ai-as)*TS()>=RR()*TS()->h>=hMIN()+RR()*(t-trepair)|as>=sDEG()&h>=hDEG())&(fail=0&as < sDEG()->t-trepair+(TS()-c) < tREPDEG()))":
                cut("(ai-as)*TS() < RR()*TS()|!(ai-as)*TS() < RR()*TS()"); <(
                  "Use":
                    orL('L=="(ai-as)*TS() < RR()*TS()|!(ai-as)*TS() < RR()*TS()"); <(
                      "(ai-as)*TS() < RR()*TS()":
                        implyL('L=="(ai-as)*TS() < RR()*TS()->h+(0-as)*(TS()-c)>=hDEG()&as=sMAX()"); <(
                          "(ai-as)*TS() < RR()*TS()":
                            hideR('R=="[{t'=1,c'=1,h'=i-d&c<=TS()}](((ai-as)*TS() < RR()*TS()->h+(0-as)*(TS()-c)>=hDEG()&as=sMAX())&(fail=0&(ai-as)*TS()>=RR()*TS()->h>=hMIN()+RR()*(t-trepair)|as>=sDEG()&h>=hDEG())&(fail=0&as < sDEG()->t-trepair+(TS()-c) < tREPDEG()))");
                            QE,
                          "h+(0-as)*(TS()-c)>=hDEG()&as=sMAX()":
                            boxAnd('R=="[{t'=1,c'=1,h'=i-d&c<=TS()}](((ai-as)*TS() < RR()*TS()->h+(0-as)*(TS()-c)>=hDEG()&as=sMAX())&(fail=0&(ai-as)*TS()>=RR()*TS()->h>=hMIN()+RR()*(t-trepair)|as>=sDEG()&h>=hDEG())&(fail=0&as < sDEG()->t-trepair+(TS()-c) < tREPDEG()))");
                            andR('R=="[{t'=1,c'=1,h'=i-d&c<=TS()}]((ai-as)*TS() < RR()*TS()->h+(0-as)*(TS()-c)>=hDEG()&as=sMAX())&[{t'=1,c'=1,h'=i-d&c<=TS()}]((fail=0&(ai-as)*TS()>=RR()*TS()->h>=hMIN()+RR()*(t-trepair)|as>=sDEG()&h>=hDEG())&(fail=0&as < sDEG()->t-trepair+(TS()-c) < tREPDEG()))"); <(
                              "[{t'=1,c'=1,h'=i-d&c<=TS()}]((ai-as)*TS() < RR()*TS()->h+(0-as)*(TS()-c)>=hDEG()&as=sMAX())":
                                auto,
                              "[{t'=1,c'=1,h'=i-d&c<=TS()}]((fail=0&(ai-as)*TS()>=RR()*TS()->h>=hMIN()+RR()*(t-trepair)|as>=sDEG()&h>=hDEG())&(fail=0&as < sDEG()->t-trepair+(TS()-c) < tREPDEG()))":
                                hideL('L=="(iMAX()-sDEG())*TS()>=RR()*TS()");
                                auto
                            )
                        ),
                      "!(ai-as)*TS() < RR()*TS()":
                        unfold;
                        fullSimplify;
                        boxAnd('R=="[{t'=1,c'=1,h'=i-d&c<=TS()}](((ai-as)*TS() < RR()*TS()->h+(-as)*(TS()-c)>=hDEG()&as=sMAX())&(fail=0&(ai-as)*TS()>=RR()*TS()->h>=hMIN()+RR()*(t-trepair)|as>=sDEG()&h>=hDEG())&(fail=0&as < sDEG()->t-trepair+(TS()-c) < tREPDEG()))");
                        andR('R=="[{t'=1,c'=1,h'=i-d&c<=TS()}]((ai-as)*TS() < RR()*TS()->h+(-as)*(TS()-c)>=hDEG()&as=sMAX())&[{t'=1,c'=1,h'=i-d&c<=TS()}]((fail=0&(ai-as)*TS()>=RR()*TS()->h>=hMIN()+RR()*(t-trepair)|as>=sDEG()&h>=hDEG())&(fail=0&as < sDEG()->t-trepair+(TS()-c) < tREPDEG()))"); <(
                          "[{t'=1,c'=1,h'=i-d&c<=TS()}]((ai-as)*TS() < RR()*TS()->h+(-as)*(TS()-c)>=hDEG()&as=sMAX())":
                            auto,
                          "[{t'=1,c'=1,h'=i-d&c<=TS()}]((fail=0&(ai-as)*TS()>=RR()*TS()->h>=hMIN()+RR()*(t-trepair)|as>=sDEG()&h>=hDEG())&(fail=0&as < sDEG()->t-trepair+(TS()-c) < tREPDEG()))":
                            boxAnd('R=="[{t'=1,c'=1,h'=i-d&c<=TS()}]((fail=0&(ai-as)*TS()>=RR()*TS()->h>=hMIN()+RR()*(t-trepair)|as>=sDEG()&h>=hDEG())&(fail=0&as < sDEG()->t-trepair+(TS()-c) < tREPDEG()))");
                            andR('R=="[{t'=1,c'=1,h'=i-d&c<=TS()}](fail=0&(ai-as)*TS()>=RR()*TS()->h>=hMIN()+RR()*(t-trepair)|as>=sDEG()&h>=hDEG())&[{t'=1,c'=1,h'=i-d&c<=TS()}](fail=0&as < sDEG()->t-trepair+(TS()-c) < tREPDEG())"); <(
                              "[{t'=1,c'=1,h'=i-d&c<=TS()}](fail=0&(ai-as)*TS()>=RR()*TS()->h>=hMIN()+RR()*(t-trepair)|as>=sDEG()&h>=hDEG())":
                                orL('L=="fail=0|fail=1"); <(
                                  "fail=0":
                                    allL2R('L=="fail=0");
                                    fullSimplify;
                                    auto,
                                  "fail=1":
                                    allL2R('L=="fail=1");
                                    auto
                                ),
                              "[{t'=1,c'=1,h'=i-d&c<=TS()}](fail=0&as < sDEG()->t-trepair+(TS()-c) < tREPDEG())":
                                orL('L=="fail=0|fail=1"); <(
                                  "fail=0":
                                    allL2R('L=="fail=0");
                                    cut("as < sDEG()|as>=sDEG()"); <(
                                      "Use":
                                        orL('L=="as < sDEG()|as>=sDEG()"); <(
                                          "as < sDEG()":
                                            implyL('L=="0=0&as < sDEG()->t-trepair+(TS()-c) < tREPDEG()"); <(
                                              "0=0&as < sDEG()":
                                                hideR('R=="[{t'=1,c'=1,h'=i-d&c<=TS()}](0=0&as < sDEG()->t-trepair+(TS()-c) < tREPDEG())");
                                                QE,
                                              "t-trepair+(TS()-c) < tREPDEG()":
                                                unfold;
                                                fullSimplify;
                                                auto
                                            ),
                                          "as>=sDEG()":
                                            auto
                                        ),
                                      "Show":
                                        hideR('R=="[{t'=1,c'=1,h'=i-d&c<=TS()}](0=0&as < sDEG()->t-trepair+(TS()-c) < tREPDEG())");
                                        QE
                                    ),
                                  "fail=1":
                                    allL2R('L=="fail=1");
                                    auto
                                )
                            )
                        )
                    ),
                  "Show":
                    hideR('R=="[{t'=1,c'=1,h'=i-d&c<=TS()}](((ai-as)*TS() < RR()*TS()->h+(0-as)*(TS()-c)>=hDEG()&as=sMAX())&(fail=0&(ai-as)*TS()>=RR()*TS()->h>=hMIN()+RR()*(t-trepair)|as>=sDEG()&h>=hDEG())&(fail=0&as < sDEG()->t-trepair+(TS()-c) < tREPDEG()))");
                    QE
                )
            )
        )
    )
)
